      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Mathematics (Agric&amp;Envir Sci)              : Measures of central tendency and dispersion; binomial and Poisson distributions; normal, chi-square, Student's t and Fisher-Snedecor F distributions; estimation and hypothesis testing; simple linear regression and correlation; analysis of variance for simple experimental designs.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              Fall 2014, Winter 2015          </p>

